称作无限宝石
Infinity Stones.

3
00:57:35.400 --> 00:57:36.890 
这些宝石似乎
These stones, it seems,

4
00:57:37.040 --> 00:57:38.880 
只有拥有非凡的力量
can only be brandished

5
00:57:39.040 --> 00:57:42.520 
才能驾驭
by beings of extraordinary strength.

6
